<br>
&quot;I know, lets do this everyone. Every time we talk in ooc, or group or something lets put... PTG.. please talk in group.. or if we are talking in guild put... PTGL.. please talk in guild.. that way the few people who dont, can say oh DUH I didnt know I was suppose to use the means of communication that everyone else uses.&quot;<br>
<br>
Just imagine if after every sentence you type in group chat if you start saying &quot;Anyone want a mod rod? PUGC&quot;..... I think that says it all. <br>
<br>
To me, if I am LFG and someone ooc's for me to come to wherever and I see it, then fine. If I don't, and they can't figure out to send me a tell, then I wouldn't want that group anyways. <br>
<br>
All things equal.. If I am purchasing an item, and one person used PST, and other did not... I would choose the one who did not use it.<br>
